metadata.name: Faisal Al Hammadi
metadata.description:
Faisal is a Managing Partner at Further Ventures. 

Further is a venture building and investment firm. 

We partner with founders and provide capital, product, engineering, design, legal, business development, and administrative support to teams who want to build lasting technology companies with us. 

Join us as a founder, colleague, or partner in our network to receive your very own Further Avatar! Learn more at https://further.ae/about
